# Critical rules — verify before every response

## Forbidden actions

- Never assume work is complete without verification
- Never create generic folders like `controllers/`, `views/`, `services/`
- Follow **`comments.mdc`** for in-source comments and TSDoc; **`documentation.mdc`** for READMEs and `docs/`

## Required actions

- Always answer questions directly before taking action
- Always verify changes by reading the actual file output
- Always terminate JavaScript and TypeScript statements with semicolons; never omit optional semicolons (see **`typescript-style.mdc`**)
- Always use 4-space indentation (see **`project.mdc`**)
